## PHOTO ASSETS

These photos are in `/public/images/`. Reference them by these names:

| File Name | Description | Where to Use |
|-----------|-------------|-------------|
| `headshot-primary.jpg` | Natural light casual headshot (green henley, warm smile) | Homepage hero, nav bar small avatar, contact page, blog author bio |
| `dress-uniform.jpg` | Fire captain dress uniform, American flag background | About page "My Story" section |
| `family-field.jpg` | Professional golden hour family photo in field | About page hero/banner |
| `family-station.jpg` | Wife + baby in front of ladder truck | About page, bridges fire service + family |
| `headshot-formal.jpg` | Navy blazer and tie professional headshot | NMLS/compliance contexts |
| `couple-sunset.jpg` | Jacob and Christine at sunset on green lawn | About page personal section |

**Image optimization rules:**
- Always use `<Image>` from next/image with width, height, and alt text
- Use `priority` prop on above-the-fold hero images
- Use `placeholder="blur"` with blurDataURL for large images
- Serve WebP/AVIF automatically (Next.js handles this)
- Use `sizes` prop for responsive images

