## SEO REQUIREMENTS (Critical — implement on EVERY page)

### Metadata (app/layout.tsx defaults + per-page overrides)

Every page MUST have:
- Unique `<title>` tag (50-60 characters, include primary keyword + "| Jacob Shope")
- Unique `<meta name="description">` (150-160 characters, include keyword + CTA)
- Open Graph tags: og:title, og:description, og:image, og:url, og:type
- Twitter Card tags: twitter:card, twitter:title, twitter:description, twitter:image
- Canonical URL
- Appropriate robots meta (index, follow for all public pages)

### JSON-LD Structured Data

**Every page (in layout or shared component):**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Organization",
  "name": "Jacob Shope - Mortgage Loan Officer",
  "url": "https://jacobshope.com",
  "logo": "https://jacobshope.com/images/logo.png",
  "contactPoint": {
    "@type": "ContactPoint",
    "telephone": "+1-XXX-XXX-XXXX",
    "contactType": "customer service"
  },
  "sameAs": ["https://instagram.com/jlshopeloans"]
}
```

**Homepage — LocalBusiness:**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "LocalBusiness",
  "name": "Jacob Shope - Mortgage Loan Officer",
  "description": "Charlotte NC mortgage loan officer and fire department captain helping families build wealth through homeownership.",
  "address": {
    "@type": "PostalAddress",
    "addressLocality": "Charlotte",
    "addressRegion": "NC",
    "postalCode": "XXXXX",
    "addressCountry": "US"
  },
  "geo": { "@type": "GeoCoordinates", "latitude": "35.2271", "longitude": "-80.8431" },
  "areaServed": [
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Charlotte" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Huntersville" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Cornelius" },
    { "@type": "City", "name": "Mooresville" },
    { "@type": "State", "name": "North Carolina" }
  ],
  "priceRange": "$$"
}
```

**About page — Person:**
```json
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "Jacob Shope",
  "jobTitle": "Mortgage Loan Officer",
  "worksFor": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Mpire Financial" },
  "image": "https://jacobshope.com/images/headshot-primary.jpg",
  "sameAs": ["https://instagram.com/jlshopeloans"]
}
```

**FAQ pages — FAQPage schema** (generate dynamically from Q&A data)

**Blog posts — Article schema** (generate from MDX frontmatter)

**Calculator pages — WebApplication schema**

### Technical SEO Checklist

- [ ] next-sitemap configured to auto-generate sitemap.xml and robots.txt
- [ ] All images have descriptive alt text (not "image1" — describe what's in the photo)
- [ ] One H1 per page, logical H2→H3 hierarchy
- [ ] Internal links between related pages (loan programs ↔ calculators ↔ blog posts ↔ service areas)
- [ ] Breadcrumbs on all sub-pages (with BreadcrumbList schema)
- [ ] Custom 404 page with helpful links
- [ ] No orphan pages (every page reachable from navigation or internal links)
- [ ] All external links use rel="noopener noreferrer" and target="_blank"
- [ ] Page load target: Lighthouse Performance 95+, Accessibility 100, Best Practices 100, SEO 95+

