## COMPLIANCE REQUIREMENTS (Mortgage Industry — Non-Negotiable)

These MUST appear on EVERY page of the site:

1. **NMLS# 2090979** — visible in footer on every page
2. **Equal Housing Lender** logo/icon — visible in footer on every page
3. **NMLS Consumer Access** link — link to https://www.nmlsconsumeraccess.org/ in footer
4. **Mpire Financial** — company name and NMLS# in footer
5. **Rate disclaimers** — wherever rates are displayed, include disclaimer text about rates being subject to change

The footer compliance line should read:
"Jacob Shope | NMLS# 2090979 | Mpire Financial NMLS# 2090979 | Equal Housing Lender"
with the Equal Housing Lender icon and a link to NMLS Consumer Access.

---

## MOBILE-FIRST REQUIREMENTS

- All layouts designed for 375px width first, then responsive up
- Touch targets: minimum 44x44px for all interactive elements
- Sticky mobile header with hamburger + "Call" button + "Get a Quote" CTA
- Bottom-anchored floating CTA on mobile: "Get a Free Quote" or click-to-call
- Calculator inputs: Use range sliders instead of (or in addition to) number inputs
- Forms: Use appropriate input types (tel, email) for mobile keyboards
- Font size: minimum 16px body text (prevents iOS zoom on input focus)
- No horizontal scroll on any viewport
- Images: serve appropriately sized images via Next.js Image srcset
- Test at: 375px, 414px, 768px, 1024px, 1280px, 1440px

