## INITIAL SETUP COMMANDS

```bash
npx create-next-app@latest jacob-shope-mortgage --typescript --tailwind --eslint --app --src-dir=false --import-alias="@/*"
cd jacob-shope-mortgage
npx shadcn@latest init
npm install lucide-react recharts react-hook-form @hookform/resolvers zod next-sitemap
npm install -D @types/node
```

Then install shadcn components as needed:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button card accordion input label select textarea badge separator sheet dialog
```

